dxf2svg.util
Class Dxf2SvgConstants

java.lang.Object
  dxf2svg.util.Dxf2SvgConstants
public final class Dxf2SvgConstants
extends java.lang.Object

This class represents all of the constants that are required for the Dxf2Svg conversion process. The class is not instantialable, all variables are called via calls to static values. This class may not be sub-classed.

Version:
0.02 - November 15, 2002
Author:
Andrew Nisbet

TAIL

public static final int TAIL
These control where any supplied partial list should appear. If the list ordering is HEAD then the list contains all the layers that must be drawn before any other. TAIL means that all not on the list must be drawn first then the layer list in order are to be rendered last, and in the supplied order. The default is TAIL for convience.
